results.name: Triangle read by rows in which row n lists the parts > 1 of the n-th region of the shell model of partitions, with a(1) = 1.
comment: For the definition of "region of n" see A206437. See also A186114. Row n lists the largest part and the parts > 1 of the n-th region of the shell model of partitions. Also 1 together with the numbers > 1 of A206437.
link: Omar E. Pol, Illustration of the seven regions of 5
Omar E. Pol, Illustration of the partitions and regions of n, for n = 1..12
xref: Column 1 is A141285. Records give A000027. The n-th record is T(A000041(n),1).
